<div>
    <t t-set="access_token" t-value="object.rating_get_access_token()" data-oe-t-inline="true"></t>
    <t t-set="partner" t-value="object.rating_get_partner_id()" data-oe-t-inline="true"></t>
    <table style="box-sizing:border-box;border-collapse:collapse;width:100%; margin:0;" width="100%" cellspacing="0"
           cellpadding="0" border="0">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td style="font-size: 14px;" valign="top">
                    <t t-if="partner.name" data-oe-t-group="0" data-oe-t-selectable="true"
                       data-oe-t-group-active="true">
                        Hello <t t-out="partner.name or ''" data-oe-t-inline="true" oe-keep-contenteditable=""
                                 contenteditable="false">Brandon Freeman</t>,
                        <br>
                        <br>


                        <p style="margin:0px 0 12px 0;box-sizing:border-box;">This automatic message informs you that we
                            have solved your
                            ticket

                            <span style="color: #444b5a;font-size: 14px">"</span>
                            <strong style="box-sizing:border-box;font-weight: 500;background-color: rgba(36, 154, 255, 0.16) ;color: #444b5a;font-size: 14px">
                                Table legs are unbalanced
                            </strong>
                            <span style="color: #444b5a;font-size: 14px">"</span>

                            . We hope that the services provided have met your
                            expectations. If you have any questions or comments, don't hesitate to reply to
                            this e-mail to re-open your ticket.
                        </p>
                    </t>
                    <t t-else="" data-oe-t-selectable="true" data-oe-t-group="0" data-oe-t-inline="true">
                        Hello,
                        <br>
                    </t>&nbsp;<br>
                    <br>Please take a moment to rate our services related to the ticket "<strong
                        t-out="object.name or ''" style="box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:500;"
                        oe-keep-contenteditable="" contenteditable="false">Table legs are unbalanced</strong>"
                    <br>

                    <p style="margin:0px 0 12px 0;box-sizing:border-box;">
                        <br>
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0px 0 12px 0;box-sizing:border-box;">
                        <br>
                    </p>
                    <t t-if="object.rating_get_rated_partner_id().name" data-oe-t-group="1" data-oe-t-selectable="true"
                       data-oe-t-group-active="true" data-oe-t-inline="true">
                        assigned to <strong t-out="object.rating_get_rated_partner_id().name or ''"
                                            style="box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:500;" oe-keep-contenteditable=""
                                            contenteditable="false">Mitchell Admin</strong>.
                    </t>
                    <t t-else="" data-oe-t-selectable="true" data-oe-t-group="1" data-oe-t-inline="true">
                        .
                        <br>
                    </t>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="text-align: center;">
                    <table summary="o_mail_notification"
                           style="box-sizing:border-box;border-collapse:collapse;width:100%; margin: 32px 0px 32px 0px;"
                           width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="font-size: 14px;">
                                    <strong style="box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:500;">Tell us how you feel about
                                        our service
                                    </strong>
                                    <br>
                                    <span style="text-color: #888888">(click on one of these smileys)</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="font-size: 14px;">
                                    <table style="box-sizing:border-box;border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;text-align:center;margin-top:24px;"
                                           width="100%">
                                        <tbody>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <a t-attf-href="/rate/{{ access_token }}/5"
                                                       style="text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box;background-color:transparent;color:inherit;">
                                                        <img alt="Satisfied" src="/rating/static/src/img/rating_5.png"
                                                             title="Satisfied"
                                                             style="border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;vertical-align:middle;"
                                                             width="69" height="69">
                                                    </a>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <a t-attf-href="/rate/{{ access_token }}/3"
                                                       style="text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box;background-color:transparent;color:inherit;">
                                                        <img alt="Okay" src="/rating/static/src/img/rating_3.png"
                                                             title="Okay"
                                                             style="border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;vertical-align:middle;"
                                                             width="69" height="69">
                                                    </a>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <a t-attf-href="/rate/{{ access_token }}/1"
                                                       style="text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box;background-color:transparent;color:inherit;">
                                                        <img alt="Dissatisfied"
                                                             src="/rating/static/src/img/rating_1.png"
                                                             title="Dissatisfied"
                                                             style="border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;vertical-align:middle;"
                                                             width="69" height="69">
                                                    </a>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </tbody>
                                    </table>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="font-size: 14px;" valign="top">
                    We appreciate your feedback. It helps us to improve continuously.
                    <br>
                    <span style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.5; color: #454748;">This customer
                        survey has been sent because your ticket has been moved to the stage
                        <b t-out="object.stage_id.name or ''" style="box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:500;"
                           oe-keep-contenteditable="" contenteditable="false">In Progress
                        </b>
                    </span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
